    "_comment_env_script": "Required. Source before benchmarks: export RCCL_TESTS_BUILD_DIR, ROCM_HOME, MPI_HOME; extend PATH/LD_LIBRARY_PATH (e.g. RCCL_HOME). Multi-node runs require MPI_HOME. NCCL/UCX/plugin tuning belongs here only — not in JSON."
